comments.message:
These lines are needed for both FRU implementations except below few lines 

"
  if (isMuxBus(bus) && address == busIface.first.second &&
     (getFRUInfo(
      static_cast<uint8_t>(busIface.first.first),
      static_cast<uint8_t>(busIface.first.second)) ==
      getFRUInfo(static_cast<uint8_t>(bus),
      static_cast<uint8_t>(address))))
      {
            // This device is already added to the lower numbered
            // bus, do not replicate it.
            return;
      }

"

The above lines of the code is needed for only i2c based fru. So skipped with IpmbFlag. Other than these lines are needed for both FRU implementations.

Without this block of code in IPMB FRU, it does not generates the dbus object. Mainly these codes does the fru dbus object generation.
